.DT
mail_count
Disk World creator help
mail_count

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
mail_count -  This method returns a 2 item array for the amount of mail in a persons inbox.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
int * mail_count(string pname)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^pname%^RESET%^ - the players name.
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
a two item array.
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/obj/handlers/folder_handler.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method returns a 2 item array for the amount of mail in a persons
inbox.  This first index is the total number of messages and the second
is the number that are unread.

.EP

